notes.text: sap.m.Select: Enhanced error handling
We now ensure that the correct instance of the plugin and control is set within the UploadSetWithTable plugin
We've now improved the image scaling and carousel preview for UploadSetwithTable
sap.m.InputBase: Redundant announcement on error state removed
sap.m.Input, sap.m.ComboBoxBase: Tests on macOS corrected
We now ensure that the download API of UploadsetwithTable handles the blob file type responses for the files that are to be downloaded
sap.m ScrollContainer: unstable QUnit tests are now fixed
sap.m.RatingIndicator: Correct value and UI sync during fast drag interactions
We've now introduced customPageContenthandler property hook within the FilePreviewDialog control to display custom content for unsupported file types
sap.m.ActionSheet: Close popup on tab next / previous
sap.ui.unified.Calendar: range selection continues across pickers
sap.m.Popover: Redundant horizontal scrollbar is now removed from Firefox
sap.m.Tokenizer: Adjust popover width according to visual specifications
core.Popup: make Popup.Dock enum have identical key and value
sap.m.MultiInput: check maxTokens when pasting tokens
sap.m.Wizard: Open ActionSheet when 1 title is truncated
sap.m.Image: DOMPurify fix
sap.m.MultiComboBox: Visual tests corrected
sap.m.SinglePlanningCalendar: now marker announcement is removed as part of the region
sap.m.Tokenizer: Prevent Scrolling upon Token delete
